  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nDealers are currently sitting right at the GEX flip (6567 vs 6567 spot) and will aggressively sell any push toward the massive 6580 gamma wall (+28B), creating a strong ceiling effect as they hedge their long gamma positions. The PIN regime with such concentrated positive gamma above means price action should remain range-bound with dealers providing natural resistance on rallies and support on dips toward 6500 negative gamma. Watch for rejection at 6580 and potential mean reversion back toward 6567 flip, with the wall break event suggesting recent volatility as spot tested these critical hedging levels.",
